# 🔍 Web Application Scanning (WAS) with Qualys

## 📌 Project Overview
This project showcases dynamic application security testing (DAST) using **Qualys WAS**. It includes scanning of web applications and APIs, vulnerability management, report generation, and integration with tools like Burp Suite.

---

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
- **Qualys Web Application Scanning (WAS)**
- **Burp Suite**
- **Swagger / OpenAPI**
- **Custom API Testing**
- **DNS Override & Path Fuzzing**

---

## ✅ Key Features Demonstrated

### 🔐 Web & API Scanning
- Web app and API vulnerability scanning
- QID analysis (Confirmed, Potential, Sensitive, Informational)
- Progressive scanning and SmartScan
- Crawl scope configuration
- Malware monitoring setup

### 🧪 API Testing
- API endpoint configuration
- Swagger integration
- Path fuzzing rules
- DNS override for non-production testing

### 🔄 Scan Configuration & Execution
- Option profile setup and tuning
- Launching discovery scans and maps
- Bulk editing web application settings
- Enhanced crawling and crawl script capture

### 🔑 Authentication & Crawl Scripts
- Standard login configuration
- Authentication record creation and editing
- Crawl script capturing and reuse

### 📊 Reporting & Analysis
- Scan Reports
- Web Application Reports
- Scorecard Reports
- Catalog Reports
- Asset grouping using Tags
- Search Lists using static and dynamic QIDs

### 🧩 Integration
- Integration with **Burp Suite** for manual testing workflows

---


